text: 190 South LaSalle Street is a 573 ft (175m) tall skyscraper in Chicago, Illinois. It was completed in 1987 and has 40 floors.190 South LaSalle, Chicago, U.S.A. | Emporis.com Johnson/Burgee Architects designed the building, which is the 57th tallest building in Chicago.190 South LaSalle, Chicago - SkyscraperPage.com ==Related pages== *List of tallest buildings in Chicago ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Skyscrapers in Chicago Category:1987 establishments in Illinois
